name: testCreateBudgetsAndCorrectForOverspending
description: TC_06.000.03 Validate create budgets with 'Add an amount every period and correct for overspending'
descriptionHtml: TC_06.000.03 Validate create budgets with 'Add an amount every period and correct for overspending'

testStage.description: TC_06.000.03 Validate create budgets with 'Add an amount every period and correct for overspending'

steps.name: Click on 'Create' button in the middle
Enter new valid name into the 'Name' field
In the 'Auto-budget' selector, select 'Add an amount every period and correct for overspending'
Enter new valid numbers into the 'Auto-budget amount' field
To the right of the budget name there is a calendar icon, when you hover over it, it the following text appears: The budget amount will increase periodically and will correct for overspending
